data.description: Sunset Subdivision has another beauty.  Home offers a 2 story, 4 bedroom, 2 .5 bathrooms, with a bonus room upstairs,.   The  laundry room down stairs with the 2 car garage.   Extremely Spacious & Move-in Ready!! Laminate wood floors in oversized Living Dining area. Ceramic tile in large and spacious Kitchen / Dining area. Generous sized back yard, with deck  and mature trees. Home also has solar panels. Conveniently located Less than 10 minutes from Lackland AFB/ 5 mins from 1604 & Hwy 90. 3-7 minutes from schools.
